  <abstract language="en" script="Latn">
    <p>This document defines the "xml2rfc" version 2 vocabulary: an XML-based language used for writing RFCs and Internet-Drafts.</p>
    <p>Version 2 represents the state of the vocabulary (as implemented by several tools and as used by the RFC Editor) around 2014.</p>
    <p>This document obsoletes RFC 2629.</p>
